{"tid":269871,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"［隨便台］[開CAM開台]開台打DEAD BY DAYLIGHT","createTime":"2017-06-04T03:04:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-04T10:40:11.000Z","uid":89382,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"18393d5da92b67c480acb3d9262655088079399d","tid":269871,"uid":89382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T03:04:39.000Z","msg":"Twitch : <a href=\"https://www.twitch.tv/justin_yu_1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.twitch.tv%2Fjustin_yu_1&d=cdmwvmwU9HO87znw5NV9MXIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=8691acc9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.twitch.tv/justin_yu_1</a><br />\nTwitch桌面app : <a href=\"https://app.twitch.tv/servers/Lz96Me\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapp.twitch.tv%2Fservers%2FLz96Me&d=cdmwvmwU9HO87znw5NV9MXIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=8937977f\" target=\"_blank\">https://app.twitch.tv/servers/Lz96Me</a><br />\nYoutube : <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCFNLF-gKhVFb_AeUzQsD-aQ/featured\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCFNLF-gKhVFb_AeUzQsD-aQ%2Ffeatured&d=cdmwvmwU9HO87znw5NV9MXIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=e542693e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCFNLF-gKhVFb_AeUzQsD-aQ/featured</a><br />\nFacebook : <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/隨便台-355532761277816/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F%E9%9A%A8%E4%BE%BF%E5%8F%B0-355532761277816%2F&d=cdmwvmwU9HO87znw5NV9MXIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=086b8c55\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/隨便台-355532761277816/</a><br />\nLINE : <a href=\"https://line.me/R/ti/p/@snp0516q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fline.me%2FR%2Fti%2Fp%2F%40snp0516q&d=cdmwvmwU9HO87znw5NV9MXIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=633516ae\" target=\"_blank\">https://line.me/R/ti/p/@snp0516q</a><br />\n<br />\nDead by daylight呢隻GAME,係一隻4 VS 1既GAME,4個人類一邊維修發電機一邊避開個殺手,維修夠發電機開大門走佬;玩殺手既就係盡量殺D人,唔俾佢地走到佬<br />\n<br />\n可惜,呢隻GAME,外國好多人玩,偏偏淨係香港冇人玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好多係身在外國既香港人,都同我講呢隻GAME外國係勁多人玩,普遍香港人個STEAM都設定係香港,所以香港人買左,馬上開GAME,幾乎係肯定冇場,因為香港SER根本冇人,已經真係有玩開GAME既人,都已經轉哂SER去其他國家玩,而依家最多人既SER而又唔會太LAG既地方,係轉去台灣泰國日本哈薩克呢D地方既SER玩<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/HdDRQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FHdDRQ.jpg&h=300ec0a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n由於係香港開CAM開台而又玩呢隻GAME既人,係得我一個台,所以呢隻GAME官方果邊都俾左呢一件twitch台台主先有既SKIN我,<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t31.0-8/16665881_781048895392865_7174868728788210755_o.jpg?oh=77d2297321dacb84b71d369393e79c2b&amp;oe=593238E6\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft31.0-8%2F16665881_781048895392865_7174868728788210755_o.jpg%3Foh%3D77d2297321dacb84b71d369393e79c2b%26oe%3D593238E6&h=385eb1ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t31.0-8/16797126_781048898726198_8047297476270724355_o.jpg?oh=2f5a4bf342f0bc469c7ca8774e4a607b&amp;oe=5941D525\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft31.0-8%2F16797126_781048898726198_8047297476270724355_o.jpg%3Foh%3D2f5a4bf342f0bc469c7ca8774e4a607b%26oe%3D5941D525&h=6384d9ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/vHoXA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FvHoXA.jpg&h=1fb87b30&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hHk7eR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhHk7eR.jpg&h=f109db8a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n下面呢個係隨便台Official LINE群,有咩突發消息,開台通知,我都會係呢度公布<br />\n<img src=\"http://qr-official.line.me/L/aqio2VXZLo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fqr-official.line.me%2FL%2Faqio2VXZLo.png&h=03fd5638&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"98ffce97bb6ecc14ec2181b5346f5162df6993a0","tid":269871,"uid":89382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyT